snippet: Monta Ellis hit a wild, fall-away jumper at the buzzer, lifting the Dallas Mavericks over the Milwaukee Bucks 107-105 on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: Ellis Hits Shot at Buzzer, Mavericks Beat Bucks
headline.main: Ellis Hits Shot at Buzzer, Mavericks Beat Bucks

lead_paragraph: Monta Ellis hit a wild, fall-away jumper at the buzzer, lifting the Dallas Mavericks over the Milwaukee Bucks 107-105 on Wednesday night.
